RICHMOND COUNCIL OFFERING EU PASSPORT CHECKING SERVICE
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    European nationals living in Richmond upon Thames are now able
    to use a new Passport Return Service available at the Council's
    register office.

    Last year, Richmond Council agreed a package of measures to support
    the borough's European residents in light of the Government's
    overall plans to protect the rights of EU citizens in the UK, once
    the country leaves the EU.

